#### Updated `saveLinks` function:
Since we are now passing a map (`URL -> Title`), we update the saving logic to format the text file nicely.

```go
func saveLinks(fullURL string, discovered map[string]string) error {
    if len(discovered) == 0 {
        return nil
    }

    onionAddress := extractOnionAddress(fullURL)
    linkDir := fmt.Sprintf("%s/%s/discovered_links", BaseOutputDir, onionAddress)
    _ = os.MkdirAll(linkDir, 0755)

    filename := generateFilenameForFile(fullURL)
    filePath := filepath.Join(linkDir, fmt.Sprintf("%s_links.txt", filename))

    var lines []string
    for link, title := range discovered {
